# Vercel uploads the WHOLE repo (it has to — web/ imports ../../shared), and it
# does not honour .gitignore. Without this it tries to read build artefacts and
# dies: `.anchor/test-ledger/admin.rpc` is a UNIX SOCKET left by the local Solana
# validator, and a socket is not a regular file — hence `Unknown system error -102`.
#
# None of this is needed to build the web app.

# Solana / Anchor build output and local validator state
target
.anchor
test-ledger
.surfpool
**/*.so

# server-side services — the web app only needs shared/
keeper
api
db
programs
migrations
scripts
tests
docs
backups

# never upload these
node_modules
**/node_modules
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
keeper/data
